# GPG Public Keys for Release Verification

This file contains the GPG public keys used to sign electrs releases.

## How to Import

```bash
# Import from this file
curl -sL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/OPCAT-Labs/electrs/main/KEYS | gpg --import

# Or download and import manually
gpg --import KEYS
```

## How to Verify Releases

After importing the key, verify release signatures:

```bash
# Download release files
wget https://github.com/OPCAT-Labs/electrs/releases/download/v3.3.0/SHA256SUMS
wget https://github.com/OPCAT-Labs/electrs/releases/download/v3.3.0/SHA256SUMS.asc

# Verify signature
gpg --verify SHA256SUMS.asc SHA256SUMS
```

---

## Release Signing Key

**Note**: The actual GPG public key will be added here once generated.

To generate and add the key, follow the instructions in `docs/GPG_SETUP.md`.

The key should be generated with:
- Key type: RSA 4096 bits
- Name: OPCAT Labs Release Signing
- Purpose: Signing electrs binary releases

Once generated, the public key block will be appended below this section.

